"Sasirekha is the bride"

2025
02:37:43,241 --> 02:37:46,315
"We all are happy that"

2026
02:37:46,592 --> 02:37:50,159
"Abhimanyu is the bridegroom"

2027
02:37:50,485 --> 02:37:51,490
"Sasirekha is the bride"

2028
02:37:56,238 --> 02:38:02,225
[chanting]

2029
02:38:10,665 --> 02:38:15,437
For me...
For me...

2030
02:38:16,262 --> 02:38:18,306
-Who are they?
-Our brothers!

2031
02:38:19,270 --> 02:38:25,201
For me...
For me...

2032
02:38:38,210 --> 02:38:39,774
What's your objection?
Remove the screen.

2033
02:38:40,441 --> 02:38:42,648
You mustn't say like
that, they may feel bad.

2034
02:38:42,705 --> 02:38:44,467
I don't care, I'm the groom.

2035
02:38:44,713 --> 02:38:46,152
I've every right to see the bride.

2036
02:38:46,245 --> 02:38:47,985
Grandpa, father-in-law,
get the screen removed.

2037
02:38:52,218 --> 02:38:53,346
What's your problem, son?

2038
02:38:53,412 --> 02:38:55,030
Why a screen hurdle between
me and the bride?

2039
02:38:55,322 --> 02:38:55,925
Get it removed.

2040
02:38:56,480 --> 02:38:57,901
What is he saying?

2041
02:38:58,161 --> 02:39:01,870
Nothing, it's not our tradition
to hold the screen for so long.

2042
02:39:02,034 --> 02:39:02,458
That's it.

2043
02:39:02,836 --> 02:39:06,524
But I think following our
traditions in our place is justified.

2044
02:39:06,763 --> 02:39:10,636
Which ever place it may be,
let it be done as they wish.

2045
02:39:10,817 --> 02:39:13,211
That's what I'm saying. Remove the screen.

2046
02:39:16,410 --> 02:39:18,855
Wonderful, Karna!
Our boy has established our supremacy.

2047
02:39:19,313 --> 02:39:22,689
I've told you long ago that
Lakshmana has more pride than father.

2048
02:39:23,319 --> 02:39:27,268
Karna, I feel pity on
seeing Krishna's predicament.

2049
02:39:27,712 --> 02:39:30,601
It's not yet over, the worse has to come.

2050
02:39:32,705 --> 02:39:34,954
Carry on the function
according to our traditions.

2051
02:39:35,267 --> 02:39:36,529
As you say, okay.

2052
02:39:36,852 --> 02:39:39,263
First the bride and groom
must stamp each other's feet,

2053
02:39:39,339 --> 02:39:40,983
after that pressing hand.

2054
02:39:41,129 --> 02:39:43,130
Shastri, what's that nonsense?

2055
02:39:43,213 --> 02:39:49,092
My lord, you must stamp on the toe of
the bride's left leg with your right leg.

2056
02:39:49,200 --> 02:39:50,512
Well, I'm ready for it.

2057
02:39:52,011 --> 02:39:56,303
You mustn't feel so shy.
You must also do it to him.

2058
02:39:56,543 --> 02:39:59,086
What if he gets angry?

2059
02:40:00,253 --> 02:40:02,363
Why would I get angry? I'm ready for it.

2060
02:40:03,811 --> 02:40:09,780
[chanting]

2061
02:40:23,042 --> 02:40:26,870
-Now, the bride must press your toe.
-No objection.

2062
02:40:32,489 --> 02:40:38,168
Ouch! Oh my God!

2063
02:40:38,439 --> 02:40:39,692
You killed me... killed me...

2064
02:40:40,014 --> 02:40:41,924
What about you when you stamped my toe?

2065
02:40:42,777 --> 02:40:45,664
Shastri and Sharma, I have to press
the hand, right? Tell her to do it.

2066
02:40:46,114 --> 02:40:49,039
-You know to vedic science too, right?
-Yes, I do.

2067
02:41:00,844 --> 02:41:04,097
-Now, bride must press your hand.
-No need.

2068
02:41:04,148 --> 02:41:06,466
No, you mustn't say no.
Give your hand to her.

2069
02:41:10,709 --> 02:41:16,685
[bones cracking]
Ouch! Oh no!

2070
02:41:19,210 --> 02:41:22,697
-My hand!
-What do you want?

2071
02:41:23,631 --> 02:41:24,878
-I want turmeric-rice to bless.
-Turmeric rice to bless?

2072
02:41:24,886 --> 02:41:26,106
It's last in the program.

2073
02:41:27,576 --> 02:41:29,378
What's all this, Krishna?

2074
02:41:29,487 --> 02:41:31,391
Modern time youth are like that, brother.

2075
02:41:32,290 --> 02:41:36,055
Son-in-law, my daughter is little scared,

2076
02:41:36,328 --> 02:41:38,821
do it little slowly.

2077
02:41:39,568 --> 02:41:40,805
If scared, she can't be a brave wife.

2078
02:41:41,030 --> 02:41:42,555
Shastri and Sharma, continue.

2079
02:41:43,385 --> 02:41:46,558
Wow uncle! He gave a
good repartee to Krishna.

2080
02:41:49,174 --> 02:41:52,208
Keep this jaggery and cumin
seeds on the bride's head. [chanting]

2081
02:41:52,253 --> 02:41:52,755
I know.

2082
02:42:01,065 --> 02:42:02,698
[gibbers]

2083
02:42:03,016 --> 02:42:06,969
Monkey... Monkey
Father, monkey...

2084
02:42:07,078 --> 02:42:10,116
-What's this, Lakshmana?
-Monkey!

2085
02:42:10,345 --> 02:42:12,269
-What is it?
-Monkey, grandpa.

2086
02:42:12,795 --> 02:42:13,362
Come with me.

2087
02:42:22,363 --> 02:42:25,580
Why are you calling
a beautiful girl as monkey?

2088
02:42:26,279 --> 02:42:27,713
Is it time to romance?

2089
02:42:28,668 --> 02:42:29,125
Go ahead.

2090
02:42:35,615 --> 02:42:36,720
Keep it on her head.
[chanting]

2091
02:42:52,435 --> 02:42:57,917
[sneezes]

2092
02:43:06,438 --> 02:43:06,904
[sneezes]

2093
02:43:07,243 --> 02:43:09,118
Can't you hold it back?

2094
02:43:09,682 --> 02:43:11,401
Go ahead, finish it.
[sneezes]

2095
02:43:15,108 --> 02:43:15,614
[sneezes]

2096
02:43:17,696 --> 02:43:21,871
I think it is due to change of water.
These sneezes doesn't mean anything.

2097
02:43:22,450 --> 02:43:23,864
Carry on.

2098
02:43:24,084 --> 02:43:27,303
-Pity! Change of water.
-Pity!

2099
02:43:39,480 --> 02:43:42,196
[wedding percussions]

2100
02:43:43,193 --> 02:43:44,470
[roars]

2101
02:43:44,691 --> 02:43:49,851
Oh my God! Tiger! Tiger!
Father, tiger...

2102
02:43:50,044 --> 02:43:53,584
-What's this Lakshmana?
-Tiger...

2103
02:43:53,718 --> 02:43:56,048
-It's not tiger, he's Krishna.
-Yes, son-in-law.

2104
02:43:58,293 --> 02:44:00,698
Mother! What's this humiliation?

2105
02:44:01,022 --> 02:44:03,316
I don't know, dear.
I don't know what sin I've committed?

2106
02:44:03,770 --> 02:44:06,167
Didn't you see the groom earlier, dear?

2107
02:44:07,096 --> 02:44:10,631
Why didn't you tell me, Duryodhana?
Is your son having any mental issues?

2108
02:44:12,635 --> 02:44:15,486
Forgive me, our prince is a brave warrior.

2109
02:44:15,842 --> 02:44:18,394
I'm surprised to see him so scared.

2110
02:44:18,953 --> 02:44:21,885
I think it is the work of
black magic of our enemies.

2111
02:44:22,141 --> 02:44:23,532
You know its solution, right?

2112
02:44:23,938 --> 02:44:25,842
Smear sacred ash and tie an amulet.

2113
02:44:26,844 --> 02:44:27,318
Come here.

2114
02:44:29,957 --> 02:44:35,179
-This is holy armour!
-This will protect you.

2115
02:44:35,350 --> 02:44:40,541
-This is holy armour!
-This will protect you.

2116
02:44:43,795 --> 02:44:45,690
No matter what, I don't want to marry her.

2117
02:44:45,898 --> 02:44:46,883
Tiger... Tiger...

2118
02:44:47,281 --> 02:44:49,535
If you refuse,
I'll get her married to Abhimanyu.

2119
02:44:49,578 --> 02:44:52,490
-No away, I want her.
-Then, come.

2120
02:44:57,231 --> 02:45:03,230
[chanting]

2121
02:45:19,338 --> 02:45:22,083
Awe!

2122
02:45:23,734 --> 02:45:24,750
De... Devil!

2123
02:45:27,136 --> 02:45:28,908
Lakshmana...
Uncle!

2124
02:45:31,069 --> 02:45:31,545
Son...

2125
02:45:37,299 --> 02:45:41,168
Oh! Prince has fainted.

2126
02:45:41,332 --> 02:45:42,731
[screams]
Laksmana...

2127
02:45:44,202 --> 02:45:46,165
Oh! Our prince has fainted.

2128
02:45:46,470 --> 02:45:48,477
-Immediate duty?
-Get him out of it.

2129
02:45:49,067 --> 02:45:49,942
No use.

2130
02:45:50,260 --> 02:45:53,052
He'll not wake up till this
magical illusion is broken.

2131
02:45:53,981 --> 02:45:55,180
What's all this, uncle?

2132
02:45:55,761 --> 02:45:59,799
I suspected foul play when
Krishna supported this marriage.

2133
02:46:08,222 --> 02:46:09,246
Uncle... uncle...

2134
02:46:09,709 --> 02:46:12,316
Don't disturb him.
I must know the truth.

2135
02:46:12,780 --> 02:46:14,760
Sathyaki, get me the plough.

2136
02:46:15,254 --> 02:46:17,543
Calm down Balarama.

2137
02:46:18,464 --> 02:46:22,908
l swear on my dice and tell you the truth.

2138
02:46:23,365 --> 02:46:24,274
Listen.

2139
02:46:25,281 --> 02:46:28,671
We usurped kingdom of Pandavas by
cheating them in the game of dice.

2140
02:46:29,618 --> 02:46:32,595
They kept their promise
and went into exile.

2141
02:46:33,175 --> 02:46:36,031
You came rushing to punish us
on hearing this.

2142
02:46:36,185 --> 02:46:39,301
But you're a barlish innocent Yadava.

2143
02:46:40,696 --> 02:46:44,576
I know you'll easily fall for
praise and felicitation.

2144
02:46:44,867 --> 02:46:45,981
You did fall for it.

2145
02:46:46,362 --> 02:46:48,000
Though you're not equal to us,

2146
02:46:48,259 --> 02:46:50,675
do you know why we insisted on
accepting your daughter in marriage?

2147
02:46:51,226 --> 02:46:54,360
lf Pandavas attack us
after the exile period,

2148
02:46:54,625 --> 02:46:58,877
to keep you and your brother
away from joining their ranks.

2149
02:46:59,710 --> 02:47:05,213
Like as you sow so you reap,
we did got a good stick for it.

2150
02:47:06,873 --> 02:47:10,664
Krishna, these cheats shouldn't
be left with this punishment,

2151
02:47:11,184 --> 02:47:13,631
-Where's my plough?
- Brother!

2152
02:47:23,653 --> 02:47:25,441
Elder uncle, I bow to you.

2153
02:47:26,134 --> 02:47:30,147
You needn't have to strain yourself,
I'm here to finish them.

2154
02:47:31,292 --> 02:47:34,526
-Who are you?
- Me? Who am I?

2155
02:47:36,107 --> 02:47:38,641
When you were arrested by Angels,

2156
02:47:38,746 --> 02:47:42,326
Arjuna who came to release you free,

2157
02:47:42,527 --> 02:47:44,976
I'm his elder brother Bhima's son.

2158
02:47:45,449 --> 02:47:49,891
ls it you Ghatotkacha?
Karna... Dushyasana... hold him.

2159
02:47:50,766 --> 02:47:56,764
[chortles]

2160
02:48:00,906 --> 02:48:03,284
Hey you Duryodhana, Dushyasana, Karna!

2161
02:48:03,523 --> 02:48:04,580
You evil minded people!

2162
02:48:04,924 --> 02:48:07,701
Weapons are protecting their
honour by not coming out.

2163
02:48:07,801 --> 02:48:13,685
[chortles]

2164
02:48:14,091 --> 02:48:15,051
I'll teach you a lesson.

2165
02:48:15,385 --> 02:48:17,874
Lambu and Jambu show
them your powers.

2166
02:48:18,276 --> 02:48:24,229
[people shrieking]

2167
02:48:35,073 --> 02:48:38,235
Duryodhana, you were arrogant
about your wealth.

2168
02:48:38,378 --> 02:48:39,990
Watch out, what happens
to your wealth.

2169
02:48:40,213 --> 02:48:41,169
Chinnamaya!

2170
02:48:41,370 --> 02:48:44,440
[reciting spell]

2171
02:48:54,436 --> 02:49:00,347
[people shrieking]

2172
02:49:19,906 --> 02:49:25,789
[people shrieking]

2173
02:49:35,195 --> 02:49:39,691
[people shrieking] Fire...
Save us... save us...

2174
02:49:40,852 --> 02:49:42,704
Their cries are music to my ears.

2175
02:49:46,471 --> 02:49:48,488
Cowards! I'll not kill refugees.

2176
02:49:48,621 --> 02:49:53,535
Lambu and Jambu, tie the Kauravas
and dump them in Hastinapuram.

2177
02:49:54,003 --> 02:49:59,610
[reciting spell]

2178
02:50:05,125 --> 02:50:09,474
[people shrieking]

2179
02:50:17,536 --> 02:50:21,405
This is my last warning
to your evil quartet.

2180
02:50:22,116 --> 02:50:26,983
"You who have the haughtiness
because of wealth"

2181
02:50:27,418 --> 02:50:31,550
"The time is approaching where
your pride brings destruction."

2182
02:50:32,036 --> 02:50:36,255
"Go and live a life with senses."

2183
02:50:37,171 --> 02:50:38,159
"One more advise."

2184
02:50:38,871 --> 02:50:40,623
"Not only the Pandavas,"

2185
02:50:41,098 --> 02:50:43,232
"but also their crores of relatives,"

2186
02:50:43,550 --> 02:50:47,312
"and their relatives of relatives,"

2187
02:50:48,156 --> 02:50:52,099
"this is the punishment if you
go against any of them."

2188
02:50:53,795 --> 02:50:58,798
"Remember these words of Ghatotkacha."

2189
02:51:00,095 --> 02:51:05,846
"Remember these words of Ghatotkacha."

2190
02:51:17,864 --> 02:51:23,567
[chortles]

2191
02:51:25,660 --> 02:51:28,247
l bow to you,
please forgive me uncle.

2192
02:51:28,839 --> 02:51:30,026
Bless you.

2193
02:51:30,563 --> 02:51:34,324
Krishna, I never expected
Bhima's son will be so clever.

2194
02:51:34,524 --> 02:51:35,831
By the way, where's our daughter?

2195
02:51:36,462 --> 02:51:38,370
Krishna! Where is Sasi?

2196
02:51:38,979 --> 02:51:39,533
Son-in-law!

2197
02:51:40,885 --> 02:51:43,252
l bow to you.
A request to elder aunt.

2198
02:51:43,693 --> 02:51:48,475
Sasi and Abhimanyu got married
in the same fixed time in my home,

2199
02:51:48,884 --> 02:51:52,220
you must come, bless them
and be my guests.

2200
02:51:52,604 --> 02:51:54,581
Why are you still here? Let's go.

2201
02:51:55,633 --> 02:51:56,418
Come brother.

2202
02:52:15,205 --> 02:52:19,165
Sister-in-law Hidamba!
My daughter got married in your home.

2203
02:52:19,808 --> 02:52:23,020
Wherever the marriage may take
place, I don't have any objections.

2204
02:52:24,169 --> 02:52:25,429
Repeating my words to me.

2205
02:52:26,413 --> 02:52:26,890
Come dear.

2206
02:52:28,559 --> 02:52:31,939
Subadhra,
I'm handing my daughter happily to you.

2207
02:52:32,647 --> 02:52:36,289
Whatever it is, my son is
responsible for this to happen.

2208
02:52:36,490 --> 02:52:37,467
That gives me immense happiness.

2209
02:52:37,674 --> 02:52:40,773
No mother... no.
This was Lord Krishna's blessing.

2210
02:52:41,377 --> 02:52:43,250
Hail Lord Krishna!

2211
02:52:43,428 --> 02:52:47,121
"Hail absolute truth...
Hail lord reclining on serpent..."

2212
02:52:50,754 --> 02:52:54,178
"Hail destroyer of evil...
hail the saviour of poor..."

2213
02:52:57,770 --> 02:53:01,306
"Hail protector of devotees...
Hail lord of illusion..."

2214
02:53:04,926 --> 02:53:08,010
"The divine ploys you play"

2215
02:53:08,442 --> 02:53:11,609
"Whoever writes or sees them"

2216
02:53:12,001 --> 02:53:15,262
"be blessed with prosperity..."

2217
02:53:15,502 --> 02:53:18,865
"...and will stay blessed
and happy forever"

